{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893370/extras/GW_special_1.png?t=1718028080\" /><br>Imagine \u2013 what if necromancy and magic spells were no different than writing some lines of code? In GHOSTWARE you\u2019ll play as Molly, <strong>brought back to life and trapped inside of an arena shooter along with five other souls.</strong> But there is something inherently wrong with the world created by the mysterious Wizard.<br><br><strong>GHOSTWARE is a mixture of hectic retro-fps action and slower pace of the adventure games.</strong> Gather your arsenal and journey through multiple dimensions, uncovering your role in the conspiracy surrounding the creation of The Arena.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893370/extras/GW_special_2.png?t=1718028080\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Explore multiple worlds full of perils and wonders</strong><br>Your story will lead you through multiple dimensions, each fundamentally impacting the gameplay loop. Traverse the decaying cyber-afterlife conjured by the Wizard and explore various locales in the real world outside the simulation.<br><br></li><li><strong>Interact with a colourful cast of friends, foes, and everything in between</strong><br>Numerous actors are at play, each with their own motives and interactions for you to uncover. Engage with various factions, converse with fellow ghosts.<br><br></li><li><strong>Hybrid gameplay inspired by 90s FPS like Unreal and Metroidvanias</strong><br>You will find yourself immersed in a highly atmospheric journey through strange and varied environments, ranging from abandoned arenas and tropical islands to urban cityscapes, uncovering numerous secret areas hidden off the beaten path.<br><br></li><li><strong>Bring mayhem with an extensive array of guns and unlockable abilities</strong><br>The Virtual and the Real World feature their own separate array of weapons for a total of more than 12 guns. Each weapon brings its own quirks and advantages to combat encounters, adding depth and strategy to your gameplay experience.<br><br></li><li><strong>Browse the WebScape in search of secrets, find out what the world's been up to</strong><br>Embark on a journey through ancient web forums, delve into forsaken blogs, and download new abilities from suspicious links. Each new URL is a piece of the puzzle that will help you uncover what the happened in the world during your eternal slumber<br><br></li><li><strong>Extra Gamemodes</strong><br>Dive into the Arcade and enjoy custom matches against bots, where you can tailor the ruleset, select your character, and much more for a relaxed and personalized gaming experience separate from the single-player campaign.</li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893370/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1718028080","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893370/page.bg.jpg?t=1718028080","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893370/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1718028080","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893370/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1718028080","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Blood, some gore, convoluted plot."},"detailed_description":"<h1>NEW GAME FROM THE CREATOR OF GHOSTWARE:</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893370/extras/GW_special_1.png?t=1718028080\" /><br>Imagine \u2013 what if necromancy and magic spells were no different than writing some lines of code? In GHOSTWARE you\u2019ll play as Molly, <strong>brought back to life and trapped inside of an arena shooter along with five other souls.</strong> But there is something inherently wrong with the world created by the mysterious Wizard.<br><br><strong>GHOSTWARE is a mixture of hectic retro-fps action and slower pace of the adventure games.</strong> Gather your arsenal and journey through multiple dimensions, uncovering your role in the conspiracy surrounding the creation of The Arena.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893370/extras/GW_special_2.png?t=1718028080\" /><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Explore multiple worlds full of perils and wonders</strong><br>Your story will lead you through multiple dimensions, each fundamentally impacting the gameplay loop. Traverse the decaying cyber-afterlife conjured by the Wizard and explore various locales in the real world outside the simulation.<br><br></li><li><strong>Interact with a colourful cast of friends, foes, and everything in between</strong><br>Numerous actors are at play, each with their own motives and interactions for you to uncover. Engage with various factions, converse with fellow ghosts.<br><br></li><li><strong>Hybrid gameplay inspired by 90s FPS like Unreal and Metroidvanias</strong><br>You will find yourself immersed in a highly atmospheric journey through strange and varied environments, ranging from abandoned arenas and tropical islands to urban cityscapes, uncovering numerous secret areas hidden off the beaten path.<br><br></li><li><strong>Bring mayhem with an extensive array of guns and unlockable abilities</strong><br>The Virtual and the Real World feature their own separate array of weapons for a total of more than 12 guns. Each weapon brings its own quirks and advantages to combat encounters, adding depth and strategy to your gameplay experience.<br><br></li><li><strong>Browse the WebScape in search of secrets, find out what the world's been up to</strong><br>Embark on a journey through ancient web forums, delve into forsaken blogs, and download new abilities from suspicious links. Each new URL is a piece of the puzzle that will help you uncover what the happened in the world during your eternal slumber<br><br></li><li><strong>Extra Gamemodes</strong><br>Dive into the Arcade and enjoy custom matches against bots, where you can tailor the ruleset, select your character, and much more for a relaxed and personalized gaming experience separate from the single-player campaign.</li></ul>","developers":["Daev Team"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893370/header.jpg?t=1718028080","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257024123,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257024123/movie480.mp4?t=1716034510","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257024123/movie_max.mp4?t=1716034510"},"name":"GHOSTWARE - final Steam trailer","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257024123/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1716034510","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257024123/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1716034510","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257024123/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1716034510"}}],"name":"GHOSTWARE: Arena of the Dead","package_groups":[{"description":"","display_type":0,"is_recurring_subscription":"false","name":"default","save_text":"","selection_text":"Select a purchase option","subs":[{"can_get_free_license":"0","is_free_license":false,"option_description":"","option_text":"GHOSTWARE: Arena of the Dead - $14.99","packag